<p>President Trump told reporters aboard Air Force One that he will not run for vice-president in 2028, calling the idea &quot;too cute&quot; while travelling to Japan . At the same time he said he &quot;would love&quot; to run for a third presidential term, comments that raised questions because the US Constitution limits presidents to two elected terms . His remarks prompted fresh discussion about succession options within the Republican field and the legal boundaries of a potential third-term effort .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/d_TjUecvOVULoKuFg5UbqOuyo6VOvAAFiI4WaUpsM3BPTotOKZoJGDnroS1QIC1w0BdQyD1RglRD6r60SC1SldABQs9QiwMMvNMvxc0Dm1gaDvLwsbXKayn3aZfui73-2ypXlTp-Y0IaN47Wp5UopPC-PtokiTxCWXQK-XwOt6cURP2LKCzqi1QoAOop4NIW683IDGyzAAK3obtVc-ETxR2qA6ljr3l4vi4R-xUMkBfH5gC_VSNpZKpgPyDF1ASelnjS-zFTH9NzBgM3' alt='President Trump departs Washington for an Asia trip aboard Air Force One' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Succession names: Trump singled out Vice President JD Vance and Secretary of State Marco Rubio as strong potential running mates or successors .</li><li>Polling claim: He told reporters he has &quot;the best poll numbers that I&#x27;ve ever had,&quot; a comment he used to underline his political standing .</li><li>Remarks on rivals: During the gaggle he dismissed unnamed Democratic prospects with a sharp phrase, calling them &quot;low IQ,&quot; according to reports .</li></ul><blockquote>I would rule that out because it&#x27;s too cute. I think the people wouldn&#x27;t like that. It&#x27;s too cute. It wouldn&#x27;t be right. - President Donald Trump</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Trump supporters: Some backers have been urging the president to seek a third term and floated the idea of a vice-presidential run as a workaround to the two-term limit . (<a href='https://www.allsides.com/news/2025-10-27-0700/donald-trump-donald-trump-rules-out-running-vice-president-2028-too-cute'>AllSides</a>)</li><li>Legal observers: Analysts note the US two-term limit would bar another elected term and report Trump has not definitively ruled out pursuing legal options to challenge the restriction . (<a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/can-donald-trump-serve-a-third-term-as-us-president-9529600#publisher=newsstand'>NDTV</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/10/28/trump-rules-out-vp-run-in-2028-but-says-he-would-love-a-third-term'>Trump rules out VP run in 2028, but says he ‘would love’ a third term</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.allsides.com/news/2025-10-27-0700/donald-trump-donald-trump-rules-out-running-vice-president-2028-too-cute'>Donald Trump Rules Out Running for Vice President in 2028: ‘Too Cute’</a> - allsides.com</li><li><a href='https://www.firstpost.com/world/trump-says-he-would-love-to-run-for-presidency-in-2028-but-rules-out-running-for-vp-13945554.html'>Trump says he would &#x27;love to&#x27; run for presidency in 2028 but rules out running for VP</a> - firstpost.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/can-donald-trump-serve-a-third-term-as-us-president-9529600#publisher=newsstand'>Can Donald Trump Serve A Third Term As US President?</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/2025/10/28/trump-leaves-door-open-for-unprecedented-third-term-as-us-president'>Trump leaves door open for unprecedented third term as US president</a> - euronews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c797q57ple9o'>Trump does not rule out seeking third term - but says he will not use VP loophole</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://japantoday.com/category/world/trump-dismisses-2028-vp-run-as-%E2%80%98too-cute-%E2%80%99-leaves-door-open-to-third-term'>Trump dismisses 2028 VP run as ‘too cute;’ leaves door open to third term</a> - japantoday.com</li></ul>